description: The cordless pressure washer is a good helper for your cleaning work. The MANUSAGE portable pressure washer is sufficient for a variety of cleaning tasks: homes, patios, garden, lawn equipment, cars, driveways, and more. This pressure washer packs a high-quality powerful 20V motor. The MANUSAGE electric pressure washer generates up to 320 PSI of water pressure and 1.0 GPM of water flow. The electric pressure washer powered by 2000mAh battery, which can last for 20-25 minutes. The electric pressure washer has a digital display that shows how much power is left so you know when to charge it. There are 6-in-1 nozzle (0°, 15°, 25°, 40°, foam spray, rain mode) and 2 different Quick-Connect nozzles (0°, 40°) used for various cleaning projects. Interchange nozzles to go from a high-pressure 0° pencil point jet to a low-pressure 40° fan spray or apply detergent to the cleaning surface with the soap bottle for additional cleaning power. The 5m hose can be inserted into swimming pools or rivers, allowing you to bypass water restrictions. The matching filter can effectively filter impurities like leaves and silt while also extending the service life. This pressure washer attaches a stainless-steel extension spray wand to access hard-to-reach areas. Its light weight also makes it easy to carry and use on multiple occasions. Our portable pressure washer cordless comes with 30 days no risk-return and 1-year assurance, if you have any questions, please feel free to contact the aftersales services.
